gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 131, Spurs 129
gameRecap.excerpt: Sacramento defeats San Antonio, 131-129. For Sacramento, DeAaron Fox led the way with 33 points, five assists, and three steals while aided by Domantas Sabonis getting his 45th straight double-double, and 58th of the season (31 points, 17 rebounds, nine assists) in the victory. Devin Vassell recorded 30 points (four 3PM), five rebounds, and nine assists with Malaki Branham tallying 23 points (five 3PM) and four assists for San Antonio in the losing effort. Sacramento improves to 36-26, while San Antonio moves to 13-50 in the loss.
